==Useful Info==
'''Spark wasps''' are fast, flying insects with an especially nasty [[electrocution|electrical]] sting and the ability to [[blinkbolt|launch themselves as lightning bolts]] at range. Spark wasps are the insect equivalent of [[raiju]]. They are thankfully rare, only occasionally appearing in the [[Spider's Nest]] and [[the Depths]]. 

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*Spark wasps are susceptible to poison, so [[Mephitic Cloud]] is your friend, and poison [[dart]]s will deal damage to them quickly.
*Alternatively, their low [[willpower]] makes it easy to affect them with [[Hexes]] or [[status effect]]-inflicting [[wand]]s.

==History==
*Spark wasps were introduced in [[0.18]].
